## Overview Screen

- Weekly stats strip: workouts this week · volume (lb) · cardio minutes
- Deload banner: appears after 24 sessions since last deload, "Mark deloaded" dismisses it and resets the counter (saved to DataStore)
- Nav tile — Gym (primary, tall, gradient): bounceClick, accent gradient
- Nav tiles — Cardio + Trophies (secondary, side-by-side): subtler gradient, bounceClick

