## Gym — Stats tab

Accessed via the Stats tab inside the Gym screen (alongside Train).

- Totals row: total workouts · exercises logged · total PRs
- 12-week frequency heatmap: day-of-week column headers, today marker (border), legend strip (Less → More)
- Volume by muscle group chart (horizontal bars, weekly lb) — labeled "BY MUSCLE · lb"
- Strength curve: line chart of max weight per session, Y-axis labels (max/mid/min), dashed grid lines at 25%/50%/75%, legend row
- PR timeline list: recent PRs with date, exercise name, weight, reps

