## Program Definition (static, hard-coded)

All 4 days fully specified with:
- Exercise name, sets, reps, unit (dumbbell / plates / bodyweight), muscle group, difficulty
- Warmup routine (4 items per day, day-specific)
- Coaching notes per exercise
- Swap catalog: alternate exercises keyed by muscle group
- Tutorial text per exercise
- Exercise IDs: ua1–ua6, la1–la6, ub1–ub7, lb1–lb6

