## UI / Design System

- Material 3, dark theme, custom color palette
- Per-day accent colors extracted from hex strings (toAccentColor())
- bounceClick modifier: spring-animated scale (0.97×) on press, no ripple (scale is the affordance)
- Radial bloom gradients via Modifier.drawBehind (smooth fade, no hard edges)
- Linear gradients on NavTiles (primary: accent 0.28→0.10, secondary: surface→accent 0.08)
- Typography: Display / Headline / Title / Body / Label hierarchy applied consistently
- ModalBottomSheet for log sheets and session summary
- AlertDialog for destructive confirmations

